summary:
I have 20 years Account Management experience, working across all media channels with a focus on retail, experiential, POS, packaging and OOH. Previously I spent 8 years working as a Graphic Designer.

My experience has been client facing - holding a hybrid role with my responsibilities extending to project management and production. 

Throughout my career I have worked for a number of reputable agencies on brands such as Akzo Nobel, Nutricia, Toyota, Lexus, MTN cellular network, Syngenta, Ferrero, Medscheme, Clinix private hospital group, Unilever brands, McCain frozen foods, Simba, Pepsi and MTN (South Africa’s leading cellular network group).
